      'Red blood cells move more freely, improving oxygen and nutrient delivery to every cell.',
      'Addresses electromagnetic imbalances that contribute to fatigue and inflammation.',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Oxygen Ion Air Therapy',
    subtitle: 'Negative Ion Infusion for Mental Clarity & Mood',
    feel: 'A sensation of "freshness" and mental clarity — like stepping outside after a rainstorm.',
    benefits: [
      'Increases serotonin levels, improving mood, focus, and mental clarity.',
      'Opens airways and improves lung function, especially for those with indoor allergies.',
