      'Improves cellular communication, supporting coordinated repair throughout the body.',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Photon Glow™ Light Therapy',
    subtitle: 'Red & Near-Infrared Light for Mitochondrial Health',
    feel: 'A gentle, soothing warmth. Many clients find this the most relaxing part of the session.',
    benefits: [
      'Red Light (630–660nm) smooths fine lines, evens skin tone, and boosts collagen production by up to 400%.',
      'Near-Infrared (850–940nm) supports muscle recovery, joint health, and deep mitochondrial function.',
      'Addresses cellular aging at the root — not just masking it.',
    ],
  },
  {
    name: 'Chromotherapy',
    subtitle: 'Customizable Ambient Light for Emotional & Hormonal Balance',
    feel: 'Deeply calming. Choose your color based on your session goal.',
    benefits: [
      'Calming amber for grounding, cool blue for mental clarity, pink for heart-centered energy.',
