  {
    name: 'Resonance Pulse™ Therapy',
    subtitle: 'Vibration Wave for Lymphatic Drainage',
    feel: 'Like a professional lymphatic massage — without the hands.',
    benefits: [
      'Moves stagnant fluids and toxins, reducing bloating and improving overall mobility.',
      "Frequencies tuned to support bioresonance and recalibrate the body's internal rhythms.",
