              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="accordion-body px-6 pb-5 pt-2 border-t border-stone-800 bg-stone-900/50">
              <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm italic mb-3">
                <strong class="text-stone-300 not-italic">What you feel:</strong> {feel}
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
