            There's something that happens when you summit a trail you couldn't have walked six months ago.
            Lab numbers become lived experience. Gary organizes hikes to motivate each other as the group
            takes on new challenges together — no judgment, just real support.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-8">
            {[
              'Monthly guided hikes through Hill Country — beginner to advanced terrain',
              'Group accountability and peer support',
              'Post-hike check-ins and biometric review',
              'Private community channel for daily connection',
              'Exclusive to active EmpowerX3 clients',
            ].map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-sm text-stone-300">
                <span class="text-brand-400 shrink-0 mt-0.5" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
                {item}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-brand-600 text-cream-100 font-semibold hover:bg-brand-500 transition-colors">
            Join the Wolfpack
