          <span class="text-8xl block mb-5" aria-hidden="true">🐺</span>
          <p class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-cream-100 mb-2">Next Hike</p>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-4">Date TBD — check the portal or watch for Gary's message.</p>
          <a href="/portal" class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 text-sm font-medium transition-colors">View in Client Portal &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- NUTRITION & SUPPLEMENTS SECTION                                 -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section id="nutrition" class="scroll-mt-32 py-20 bg-stone-900 border-t-4 border-gold-600">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-4xl" aria-hidden="true">⚗️</span>
        <div>
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-3xl text-cream-100">Nutrition & Supplements</h2>
          <p class="text-gold-500 font-semibold text-sm">Precision Protocols Built from Your Genetic Data</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-stone-400 leading-relaxed mb-10 max-w-3xl">
        Generic supplement stacks and one-size-fits-all diets are why most people fail. Your body
        processes nutrients, responds to stress, and builds muscle differently than anyone else's —
        because your genetics are different. Every EmpowerX3 protocol starts with genetic testing
        to eliminate the guesswork entirely.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        {[
          {
            icon: '🧬',
            title: 'Genetic Testing',
            body: "We start with a comprehensive genetic panel that reveals exactly how your body processes specific nutrients, responds to stress hormones, and builds or loses muscle. Your protocol is built from this data — not a template.",
          },
          {
            icon: '🌿',
            title: 'Plant Medicine Detox',
