        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-stone-400 leading-relaxed pl-4">
          <p>You've bought the supplements. You've tried the elimination diets. You felt something for a few weeks, then plateaued. That's not a discipline problem — it's an information problem.</p>
          <p>Without knowing how your specific body methylates B-vitamins, processes fatty acids, or handles oxidative stress, you're supplementing blind. Some of what you're taking may be doing nothing. Some may be actively counterproductive for your genotype.</p>
          <p class="font-medium text-stone-200">EmpowerX3's genetic-based approach eliminates all of that. Every supplement, every dosage, every timing protocol is matched to what your body actually needs.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center mt-6 ml-4 px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg bg-gold-500 text-stone-950 font-semibold hover:bg-gold-400 transition-colors">
